high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the fridge, turn left, move forward, then turn left to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the rightmost sponge on the kitchen island.
Turn right and move forward until you reach the sink, then turn right to face it.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Turn around and go forward, then turn right at the shelves.
Put the sponge on the middle shelf, to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the fridge and turn left just before the dishwasher to face the counter.
Pick up the green sponge to the right of the paper towel roll on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink on the right near the window.
Put the sponge in the sink to the right of the bowl, rinse it for a few seconds, and pick up the sponge.
Turn around and head to the wooden shelves on the right.
Put the rinsed sponge on the right side of the middle wooden shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed sponge on a shelf.

high_descs: turn around, walk around the kitchen counter
take the green sponge from the counter
turn right, head to the sink
put the sponge in the sink, turn on the water for 3 seconds
take the sponge out of the sink
turn around, head across the kitchen, put the sponge on the shelf
anns.task_desc: wash the sponge for 3 seconds, put it on the shelf
